snippet.title: Dam Busters | OFFICIAL launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Created by by Julkip is this Game a reimagining of the Magnavox Odyssey² Game Videopac 29 - Dam Buster.
Play the aggressor and destroy the dam brick by brick using your state of the art bullet-reflecting ship.
Or maybe play the defender and command your work force to repair any damage done to your dam.
The choice is yours!

by Julkip: https://twitter.com/julkip
on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1298600/Dam_Busters/
publisher on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SpielmannSpiel
